task.summary: Improved image downloading for images from data (now images download is canceled if there is quick subsequnt request for new image associated to object). This is done to improve image loading speed when table/collection is quickly scrolled - in this case only last images for reused imageView is downloaded.

1) Added "create" method to all view components (this should allow user to create component in JS code) 2) Adapted example to new JSPlugin format 3) improved setting of "extra" data (to componentInfo)
